{"tid":1219364,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】團體指警截停視障人士　質問盲人枴杖是否攻擊性武器","createTime":"2019-06-13T19:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T21:22:31.000Z","uid":228793,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0a5ca2397f638e04a26654206a6636a6e96d5802","tid":1219364,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:39:09.000Z","msg":"連串反修訂《逃犯條例》示威觸發警民關係變得緊張，由著名失明人士莊陳有任會長的香港失明人協進會，今（13日）發出聲明，指有視障人士近日在港鐵站遭到警方截停，並查問視障人士使用的白杖（盲人枴杖）是否攻擊性武器，該會批評做法「非常荒謬」。另外，該會再次促請特區政府先暫緩有關修例草案的審議，避免社會進一步撕裂。<br />\n《香港01》已向警方查詢。<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n每年「國際白杖日」，協進會也會向公眾宣揚白杖精神&mdash;手持白杖，獨立自強。　（香港失明人協進會facebook圖片)<br />\n<br />\n香港失明人協進會指，有視障會員表示，於6月9日曾在港鐵站附近遭到警方截停，並查問視障人士使用的白杖是否攻擊性武器，「這點實在非常荒謬。」<br />\n該會稱，白杖是視障人士出行的必要工具，更是視障人士獨立自強的標誌。手執白杖，讓視障人士能探索前路，積極生活。對於警方竟截停視障人士並對白杖的用途有所懷疑，該會深感失望，認為警方必須加強前線警務人員對殘疾人士的認識。<br />\n該會並指，大批香港市民就《逃犯條例》修訂草案，透過和平遊行、罷工罷課包圍立法會及政府總部的方式向政府表達憂慮，只換來警方的暴力對待，實在令人心痛。該會再次促請特區政府先暫緩有關修例草案的審議，容許社會上有足夠的討論和細心聆聽市民各界對修例草案的意見，避免社會進一步撕裂，以回復香港的和諧穩定為首要考慮。<br />\n<br />\n轉自香港01<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340407/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%81%9C%E8%A6%96%E9%9A%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E8%B3%AA%E5%95%8F%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E6%9E%B4%E6%9D%96%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F340407%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%258C%2587%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2588%25AA%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25A6%2596%25E9%259A%259C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A3%25AB-%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E5%2595%258F%25E7%259B%25B2%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%259E%25B4%25E6%259D%2596%25E6%2598%25AF%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%2594%25BB%25E6%2593%258A%25E6%2580%25A7%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dfbpost_link%26utm_campaign%3Dnews&d=dLzfXDqznxc4YuOEPdKADabKco4j3WCMPlNn4btP894%3D&h=e81c0f8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/340407/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E6%8C%87%E8%AD%A6%E6%88%AA%E5%81%9C%E8%A6%96%E9%9A%9C%E4%BA%BA%E5%A3%AB-%E8%B3%AA%E5%95%8F%E7%9B%B2%E4%BA%BA%E6%9E%B4%E6%9D%96%E6%98%AF%E5%90%A6%E6%94%BB%E6%93%8A%E6%80%A7%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=fbpost_link&amp;utm_campaign=news</a>"},{"pid":"d1e3c4514a233702c36383a814c86f07c300afdb","tid":1219364,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e6d7c06c3c4de6317ff1f018bc7661810a5cec","tid":1219364,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:41:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b4fcab909f000aead6df8e665adda9a005cc726","tid":1219364,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b0cece65686962366ac0f3e14318089abe3683","tid":1219364,"uid":228793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T19:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"221193376f5dd4803480933cfc2b4568ba5eb063","tid":1219364,"uid":63808,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:08:25.000Z","msg":"推，開始走火入魔"},{"pid":"cce6ff42fe4f6840eac767fdac19b63e22d88a5a","tid":1219364,"uid":85586,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T20:24:34.000Z","msg":"搞弱勢社群呢啲咁危險嘅嘢都做<br />\n佢哋今次玩真心定假膠嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2154173155dabe587ba1